Name: AccountDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer account.

Name: AdFormat
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
TEXT / text
IMAGE / image
DYNAMIC_IMAGE / dynamic_image
FLASH / flash
VIDEO / video
HTML / html
AUDIO / audio
COMPOSITE / composite
PRINT / print
Notes: The underlying media format of the ad. Values can be one of the formats on the Template Ads page, or a MediaType enum.

Name: AdGroupId
Notes: The ID of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupName
Notes: The name of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed
Notes: Status of the ad group.

Name: AdNetworkType1
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
SEARCH / Search Network
CONTENT / Display Network
YOUTUBE_SEARCH / YouTube Search
YOUTUBE_WATCH / YouTube Videos
Notes: First level network type.

Name: AdNetworkType2
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
SEARCH / Google search
SEARCH_PARTNERS / Search partners
CONTENT / Display Network
YOUTUBE_SEARCH / YouTube Search
YOUTUBE_WATCH / YouTube Videos
Notes: Second level network type (includes search partners).

Name: AoiCityCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the city of the Location criterion matching the area of interest (AOI) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: AoiCountryCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the country of the Location criterion matching the area of interest (AOI) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: AoiMetroCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the metro area of the Location criterion matching the area of interest (AOI) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: AoiMostSpecificTargetId
Display Name: Most specific location target (Location of interest)
Notes: The most specific location target (Location of interest).

Name: AoiRegionCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the region of the Location criterion matching the area of interest (AOI) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignLocationTargetId
Notes: Location ID of the matching campaign criterion.

Name: CampaignName
Notes: The name of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed
Notes: The status of the Campaign.

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

VIDEO_WEBSITE_CLICKS / Website
VIDEO_CALL_TO_ACTION_CLICKS / Call-to-Action overlay
VIDEO_APP_STORE_CLICKS / App store
VIDEO_CARD_ACTION_HEADLINE_CLICKS / Cards
VIDEO_END_CAP_CLICKS / End cap
CLICK_ON_ENGAGEMENT_AD / Click on engagement ad
LOCATION_FORMAT_MAP / Map

Name: CreativeId
Notes: ID of the ad.

Name: CriteriaId
Notes: The Criterion ID.

Name: CriteriaParameters
Notes: Descriptive string for the Criterion. For more information on the format of criteria types in reports, see the Criteria prefixes section of the reporting guide.

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: Device
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Other
DESKTOP / Computers
HIGH_END_MOBILE / Mobile devices with full browsers
TABLET / Tablets with full browsers
Notes: Device type where the impression was shown.

Name: ExternalCustomerId
Notes: The Customer ID.

Name: GclId
Notes: The Google Click ID.

Name: KeywordMatchType
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
EXACT / Exact
PHRASE / Phrase
BROAD / Broad
Notes: The match type for the Keyword.

Name: LopCityCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the city of the Location criterion matching the location of presence (LOP) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: LopCountryCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the country of the Location criterion matching the location of presence (LOP) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: LopMetroCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the metro area of the Location criterion matching the location of presence (LOP) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: LopMostSpecificTargetId
Notes: The most specific location target (Physical location).

Name: LopRegionCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the region of the Location criterion matching the location of presence (LOP) associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.
